00:16:11.038 --> 00:16:12.372 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Tetta Kisaki!

00:16:12.406 --> 00:16:14.341 position:19% line:83% align:start
Always one of the
most important figures

00:16:14.374 --> 00:16:16.578 position:7% line:89% align:start
in the entire Tokyo Manji Gang

00:16:16.611 --> 00:16:19.914 position:21% line:83% align:start
and now, apparently,
its acting commander,

00:16:19.948 --> 00:16:22.884 position:16% line:83% align:start
the guy that somehow the
whole Tokyo police force

00:16:22.917 --> 00:16:24.686 position:7% line:89% align:start
could never get their hands on!

00:16:24.719 --> 00:16:27.054 position:5% line:89% align:start
Is this really that same Kisaki?

00:16:27.087 --> 00:16:28.523 position:21% line:83% align:start
-At this point
-(Takemichi gasping)

00:16:28.556 --> 00:16:31.225 position:13% line:83% align:start
we've all known each other
for quite a long time.

00:16:31.258 --> 00:16:32.392 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:32.426 --> 00:16:33.327 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:34.896 position:19% line:83% align:start
I never thought
everyone from back then

00:16:34.929 --> 00:16:36.764 position:21% line:83% align:start
would still be alive
and kicking today,

00:16:36.798 --> 00:16:38.700 position:13% line:89% align:start
much less be here with us.

00:16:38.733 --> 00:16:41.134 position:13% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi grunting warily)

00:16:41.168 --> 00:16:42.804 position:7% line:89% align:start
Are you surprised to hear that?

00:16:42.837 --> 00:16:45.138 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Uh, no, not really.

00:16:47.575 --> 00:16:49.309 position:24% line:89% align:start
Takemichi, Chifuyu.

00:16:50.512 --> 00:16:51.478 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Huh?

00:16:51.513 --> 00:16:53.013 position:33% line:89% align:start
Tell me this.

00:16:53.046 --> 00:16:54.448 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tell the truth.

00:16:54.481 --> 00:16:55.482 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Huh?

00:16:56.851 --> 00:16:58.553 position:30% line:89% align:start
Do you hate me?

00:16:58.586 --> 00:17:01.388 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi gasping)

00:17:02.557 --> 00:17:06.493 position:19% line:5% align:start
It was about this time,
only 12 long years ago,

00:17:06.528 --> 00:17:07.529 position:30% line:89% align:start
when Baji died.

00:17:07.562 --> 00:17:09.797 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Chifuyu grunting)

00:17:09.831 --> 00:17:11.900 position:7% line:89% align:start
The blame for that is all mine.

00:17:11.933 --> 00:17:14.167 position:13% line:5% align:start
(both grunting in surprise)

00:17:14.201 --> 00:17:16.638 position:13% line:5% align:start
I'm the one who planned the
Bloody Halloween battle.

00:17:16.671 --> 00:17:17.805 position:5% line:5% align:start
(Takemichi grunting in surprise)

00:17:17.839 --> 00:17:19.273 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] I already knew that,

00:17:19.306 --> 00:17:22.510 position:19% line:83% align:start
but why would he admit
it and say it out loud?

00:17:24.044 --> 00:17:27.180 position:13% line:83% align:start
I used Hanma to sweet-talk
Kazutora Hanemiya

00:17:27.949 --> 00:17:30.050 position:10% line:89% align:start
and then I created Valhalla,

00:17:31.019 --> 00:17:33.320 position:19% line:83% align:start
and then I set them up
to clash with Toman.

00:17:34.522 --> 00:17:36.456 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu] But why
would you do that?

00:17:38.860 --> 00:17:40.394 position:19% line:89% align:start
Because I wanted power!

00:17:41.428 --> 00:17:43.263 position:16% line:5% align:start
I wanted to be
respected for something.

00:17:44.364 --> 00:17:46.233 position:24% line:5% align:start
And I thought if I
stopped the fight,

00:17:46.266 --> 00:17:48.235 position:24% line:5% align:start
then everyone would
bow down to me.

00:17:48.870 --> 00:17:50.872 position:27% line:89% align:start
I was desperate.

00:17:50.905 --> 00:17:53.440 position:24% line:83% align:start
I didn't think Baji
was going to die!

00:17:53.473 --> 00:17:54.241 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Chifuyu gasping)

00:17:54.274 --> 00:17:55.543 position:21% line:5% align:start
I'm serious, Chifuyu!

00:17:56.611 --> 00:17:57.579 position:21% line:5% align:start
(Takemichi grunting)

00:17:57.612 --> 00:17:59.747 position:30% line:5% align:start
(somber music)

00:17:59.781 --> 00:18:00.782 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:18:02.115 --> 00:18:04.251 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've wanted to say
that for so long.

00:18:05.118 --> 00:18:07.454 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's our friends
who are important.

00:18:07.487 --> 00:18:10.190 position:24% line:83% align:start
After 12 years, I
finally understand.

00:18:11.059 --> 00:18:12.827 position:10% line:5% align:start
So you regret what happened?

00:18:12.860 --> 00:18:14.328 position:10% line:5% align:start
All the things you did then?

00:18:16.698 --> 00:18:19.033 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not a single day
goes by that I don't.

00:18:19.067 --> 00:18:21.335 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi grunting)

00:18:21.368 --> 00:18:24.237 position:13% line:5% align:start
You can continue to hate
me, of course, if you must,

00:18:25.405 --> 00:18:27.575 position:24% line:5% align:start
but at least have a
drink with me today.

00:18:28.241 --> 00:18:29.376 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] All right.

00:18:32.714 --> 00:18:34.849 position:19% line:5% align:start
Here's a toast to Baji.

00:18:36.584 --> 00:18:38.218 position:30% line:89% align:start
(all slurping)

00:18:38.251 --> 00:18:39.520 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi And Chifuyu] Ah.

00:18:39.554 --> 00:18:42.056 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey, uh, can I
have beer instead?

00:18:42.090 --> 00:18:43.758 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm not used to the
expensive stuff.

00:18:43.791 --> 00:18:44.726 position:21% line:89% align:start
(chuckling) Hey hey,

00:18:44.759 --> 00:18:47.528 position:16% line:83% align:start
we can't have Toman
execs talking like that!

00:18:47.562 --> 00:18:48.362 position:35% line:89% align:start
Guess not.

00:18:49.764 --> 00:18:50.999 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi coughing)

00:18:51.032 --> 00:18:52.232 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Kisaki laughing)

00:18:52.265 --> 00:18:54.569 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] Don't force yourself.

00:18:54.602 --> 00:18:56.838 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] I can't
believe this is happening.

00:18:56.871 --> 00:18:59.107 position:13% line:89% align:start
You know, maybe this future

00:18:59.139 --> 00:19:00.875 position:24% line:83% align:start
is actually pretty
awesome after all.

00:19:04.311 --> 00:19:07.882 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Kisaki] (sighing) I haven't
had this much fun in a while.

00:19:07.915 --> 00:19:09.249 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Yeah, same here.

00:19:09.282 --> 00:19:11.151 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Kisaki] Can I say
just one more thing?

00:19:11.184 --> 00:19:12.185 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Hm?

00:19:13.186 --> 00:19:15.123 position:24% line:83% align:start
When I said earlier
that I didn't think

00:19:15.155 --> 00:19:17.190 position:27% line:83% align:start
Baji was going to
die that day...

00:19:18.993 --> 00:19:21.796 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, well, I lied.

00:19:21.829 --> 00:19:22.997 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:23.031 --> 00:19:24.132 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:24.164 --> 00:19:26.199 position:7% line:89% align:start
I used Kazutora's insane anger

00:19:26.233 --> 00:19:28.368 position:10% line:89% align:start
to get Baji killed that day.

00:19:28.402 --> 00:19:32.006 position:19% line:83% align:start
And now I'm about to
finish what I started.

00:19:32.040 --> 00:19:33.641 position:21% line:83% align:start
-(Takemichi gasping)
-(suspenseful music)

00:19:33.675 --> 00:19:35.342 position:41% line:89% align:start
Oh no!

00:19:35.375 --> 00:19:38.046 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi crashing)

00:19:38.079 --> 00:19:40.548 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi gasping)

00:19:40.581 --> 00:19:42.116 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:42.150 --> 00:19:44.952 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh that's right, this is...

00:19:44.986 --> 00:19:46.420 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey, I can't move!

00:19:47.588 --> 00:19:50.091 position:24% line:83% align:start
(groaning) What the
hell's going on?

00:19:50.124 --> 00:19:52.259 position:24% line:83% align:start
(grunting) What am
I doing tied up?

00:19:52.292 --> 00:19:53.628 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Takemitchy.
-Hm?

00:19:53.661 --> 00:19:54.428 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Chifuyu?

00:19:54.461 --> 00:19:55.897 position:7% line:89% align:start
What the hell happened to you?

00:19:55.930 --> 00:19:57.799 position:7% line:89% align:start
Looks like you had a good nap.

00:19:57.832 --> 00:19:59.433 position:30% line:89% align:start
(both grunting)

00:19:59.466 --> 00:20:00.768 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hanagaki.

00:20:00.802 --> 00:20:01.602 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Kisaki!

00:20:02.670 --> 00:20:03.671 position:30% line:89% align:start
You drugged us!

00:20:04.806 --> 00:20:06.273 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi grunting)

00:20:06.306 --> 00:20:10.343 position:13% line:83% align:start
Chifuyu Matsuno, you sure
are an annoying little fly.

00:20:10.377 --> 00:20:12.412 position:10% line:83% align:start
You just couldn't forget
about something that happened

00:20:12.446 --> 00:20:16.184 position:19% line:83% align:start
12 years ago and you
kept trying to bite me.

00:20:16.216 --> 00:20:18.786 position:19% line:83% align:start
You had to get
revenge for Baji, huh?

00:20:18.820 --> 00:20:20.188 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Huh?

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:21.055 position:24% line:83% align:start
-(blow thudding)
-(Chifuyu grunting)

00:20:21.089 --> 00:20:22.590 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Stop it, Kisaki!

00:20:22.623 --> 00:20:25.258 position:7% line:89% align:start
Why not admit that it was you?

00:20:25.292 --> 00:20:27.995 position:19% line:83% align:start
The two of you together
are Judas, aren't you?

00:20:28.029 --> 00:20:29.329 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-(blow thudding)

00:20:29.362 --> 00:20:31.766 position:13% line:83% align:start
Seriously, you sure did
tell the cops a lotta shit,

00:20:31.799 --> 00:20:33.668 position:13% line:83% align:start
-you stupid dumbass!
-Stop it, Kisaki, damn you!

00:20:33.701 --> 00:20:37.370 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Stop it!
-(Chifuyu coughing)

00:20:39.040 --> 00:20:40.240 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're wrong!

00:20:40.273 --> 00:20:42.744 position:24% line:83% align:start
The cops got all
that on their own!

00:20:42.777 --> 00:20:44.411 position:27% line:89% align:start
All I ever wanted

00:20:44.444 --> 00:20:46.948 position:19% line:83% align:start
was to run you out of
Toman once and for all!

00:20:47.782 --> 00:20:49.517 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Kisaki sighing)

00:20:49.550 --> 00:20:52.352 position:13% line:83% align:start
How long are you gonna keep
chasing after Baji's shadow,

00:20:52.385 --> 00:20:54.088 position:19% line:89% align:start
you sorry little shit?

00:20:54.122 --> 00:20:56.958 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Chifuyu panting)

00:20:56.991 --> 00:20:58.760 position:16% line:89% align:start
Toman's rotten right now,

00:20:58.793 --> 00:21:00.728 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I'm the one who's
gonna change it!

00:21:01.896 --> 00:21:05.066 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're right about one
thing, I am the Judas.

00:21:05.099 --> 00:21:06.934 position:19% line:89% align:start
Takemitchy didn't know.

00:21:06.968 --> 00:21:09.971 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] Oh, Chifuyu,
don't tell me 12 years later

00:21:10.004 --> 00:21:11.304 position:7% line:89% align:start
you were still trying to avenge

00:21:11.338 --> 00:21:13.440 position:10% line:89% align:start
Baji's death all by yourself?

00:21:14.242 --> 00:21:15.442 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:21:16.177 --> 00:21:18.546 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm the one who gets to decide

00:21:18.579 --> 00:21:20.848 position:16% line:83% align:start
whether he's been
involved in this or not.

00:21:20.882 --> 00:21:22.382 position:16% line:89% align:start
(tense suspenseful music)

00:21:22.415 --> 00:21:25.253 position:5% line:89% align:start
So, Hanagaki, why are you acting

00:21:25.285 --> 00:21:28.156 position:19% line:83% align:start
like you've got no idea
what's going on here?

00:21:28.189 --> 00:21:29.557 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Huh?

00:21:29.590 --> 00:21:30.357 position:44% line:89% align:start
Well?

00:21:30.390 --> 00:21:31.491 position:27% line:89% align:start
(gunshot booming)

00:21:31.526 --> 00:21:33.393 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi screaming)

00:21:33.426 --> 00:21:35.163 position:16% line:89% align:start
You bastard, I told you,

00:21:35.196 --> 00:21:36.664 position:19% line:83% align:start
Takemitchy has nothing
to do with this!

00:21:36.697 --> 00:21:37.965 position:13% line:83% align:start
-He doesn't know anything!
-My leg!

00:21:37.999 --> 00:21:39.167 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, shut your mouth!

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:40.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
You two are
partners, aren't you?

00:21:40.268 --> 00:21:41.235 position:19% line:89% align:start
You shared everything!

00:21:41.269 --> 00:21:43.971 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi screaming)

00:21:44.005 --> 00:21:45.072 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're a lunatic.

00:21:45.106 --> 00:21:48.576 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi screaming)

00:21:48.609 --> 00:21:51.478 position:7% line:89% align:start
So, got any last words to say?

00:21:51.512 --> 00:21:54.816 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi screaming)

00:21:54.849 --> 00:21:56.083 position:35% line:89% align:start
Takemitchy.

00:21:56.117 --> 00:21:59.754 position:21% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi screaming)

00:21:59.787 --> 00:22:00.955 position:35% line:89% align:start
Takemichi!

00:22:00.988 --> 00:22:03.356 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi panting)

00:22:03.390 --> 00:22:08.296 position:13% line:83% align:start
Listen, Takemitchy, because
these are my last words.

00:22:08.328 --> 00:22:10.765 position:21% line:83% align:start
A lot has happened
these past 12 years.

00:22:10.798 --> 00:22:12.533 position:27% line:89% align:start
Mikey disappeared

00:22:12.567 --> 00:22:15.368 position:16% line:89% align:start
and Draken was executed.

00:22:15.402 --> 00:22:17.271 position:21% line:83% align:start
Before we knew it,
we'd gotten ourselves

00:22:17.305 --> 00:22:19.339 position:5% line:89% align:start
involved in some messed-up shit.

00:22:20.575 --> 00:22:23.611 position:10% line:83% align:start
And all of us made our share
of some serious mistakes,

00:22:23.644 --> 00:22:27.215 position:13% line:83% align:start
but still, down deep I know
that we haven't changed!

00:22:27.248 --> 00:22:28.883 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi gasping)

00:22:28.916 --> 00:22:32.253 position:21% line:83% align:start
So now Baji's legacy,
and Toman's as well,

00:22:32.286 --> 00:22:34.222 position:30% line:89% align:start
(somber music)

00:22:34.255 --> 00:22:35.455 position:33% line:89% align:start
they're both

00:22:37.091 --> 00:22:39.359 position:19% line:89% align:start
in your hands partner.

00:22:40.328 --> 00:22:42.196 position:21% line:83% align:start
-(gunshot booming)
-(Takemichi gasping)

00:22:42.230 --> 00:22:43.197 position:30% line:89% align:start
(body thudding)

00:22:43.231 --> 00:22:44.665 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi gasping)

00:22:44.699 --> 00:22:45.498 position:38% line:89% align:start
Chifuyu!

00:22:46.399 --> 00:22:49.670 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi sobbing)

00:22:49.704 --> 00:22:50.872 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:22:50.905 --> 00:22:53.541 position:24% line:83% align:start
This has to be some
kind of nightmare!

00:22:53.574 --> 00:22:56.310 position:19% line:83% align:start
There's no way
Chifuyu could be dead!

00:22:56.344 --> 00:22:58.145 position:30% line:89% align:start
Just like that?

00:22:58.179 --> 00:23:00.248 position:27% line:83% align:start
So how's it feel
to have the fate

00:23:00.281 --> 00:23:02.482 position:19% line:83% align:start
of all of Toman
resting in your hands?

00:23:02.516 --> 00:23:03.985 position:24% line:89% align:start
(suspenseful music)

00:23:04.018 --> 00:23:07.955 position:10% line:83% align:start
Don't worry, you're gonna be
following him soon enough.

00:23:07.989 --> 00:23:10.791 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi sobbing)

00:23:10.825 --> 00:23:13.460 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Kisaki growling)

00:23:15.196 --> 00:23:16.998 position:16% line:89% align:start
What in the hell are you?

00:23:17.031 --> 00:23:20.301 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi gasping)

00:23:20.334 --> 00:23:22.637 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is that really all
you've got, huh?

00:23:22.670 --> 00:23:26.507 position:10% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi breathing shakily)

00:23:31.012 --> 00:23:32.179 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's too bad.

00:23:32.213 --> 00:23:35.883 position:13% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi panting angrily)

00:23:38.219 --> 00:23:39.419 position:38% line:89% align:start
How sad.

00:23:40.288 --> 00:23:41.923 position:38% line:89% align:start
Farewell,

00:23:41.956 --> 00:23:42.957 position:44% line:89% align:start
hero.

00:23:44.091 --> 00:23:46.894 position:27% line:5% align:start
(gunshot booming)

